---
const rawApiBase = (import.meta.env.PUBLIC_NODE_API_BASE ?? '').trim();
const { initialView = 'analysis' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#fbf5f0] text-[#2f2a28]" data-initial-view={initialView}>
  <style is:inline>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@600;700;800&family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
  </style>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -left-24 top-16 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[#ff709f]/18 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-0 top-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-[#fff176]/25 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/3 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[#7fe6db]/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 pb-20 pt-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="font-family:'Be Vietnam Pro','Pretendard',sans-serif;">
    <section class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.92fr)_minmax(0,1.08fr)]">
      <div>
        <p class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#7fe6db]/60 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#005a54]">ManyTool AI Premium Naming</p>
        <h2 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl" style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans','Pretendard',sans-serif;">
          성명학 기반 이름풀이와 개명추천
          <span class="block text-[#a7295a] italic">한 번에 보는 프리미엄 리포트</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-[#5f5a57] sm:text-lg">
          이름풀이, 개명추천, 개명풀이를 한 화면에서 이어서 봅니다. 이름만 입력해도 시작할 수 있고, 한자까지 넣으면 수리오행과 추천 이유가 더 깊게 열립니다.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-[#f6f0ea] p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">성명학 기반 이름풀이</h3><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]">오격, 81수, 한자 의미, 오행 흐름을 묶어서 현재 이름의 강점과 보완 포인트를 읽어드립니다.</p></article>
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-[#fff7cb] p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">개명추천 6개 제안</h3><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]">추천 이름마다 한글 독음, 한자, 추천 이유, 의미 해석을 같이 보여주는 프리미엄 구성이 들어갑니다.</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section id="premium-form" class="relative rounded-[36px] bg-white/84 p-5 shadow-[0_28px_80px_rgba(48,46,43,0.08)] backdrop-blur sm:p-7">
        <div data-loading-overlay class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-20 hidden items-center justify-center rounded-[36px] bg-[#fbf5f0]/88 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="w-full max-w-md rounded-[30px] bg-white px-6 py-7 text-center shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(48,46,43,0.12)]">
            <div class="mx-auto h-7 w-7 animate-spin rounded-full border-[3px] border-[#f0d8e2] border-t-[#a7295a]"></div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-extrabold" data-loading-title>분석 준비 중</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-loading-text>이름풀이와 개명추천 결과를 순서대로 정리하고 있습니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(240px,0.8fr)]">
          <article class="rounded-[30px] bg-[#fdf7f3] p-5">
            <div class="mb-4 rounded-[24px] border border-[#ead8d2] bg-white/75 px-4 py-4 text-sm leading-7 text-[#6d6360]">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#2f2a28]">사용법</p>
              <p class="mt-2">이름만 필수입니다. 한자, 생년월일, 양력·음력, 성별은 선택 입력이며 넣을수록 분석 문구가 더 풍부해집니다.</p>
            </div>
            <form id="name-premium-form" class="space-y-4">
              <label class="block rounded-[24px] bg-white/88 p-4 ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/16"><span class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-sm font-bold">이름</span><span class="rounded-full bg-[#a7295a] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-white">필수</span></span><input name="displayName" placeholder="김민수" class="w-full rounded-[18px] border-0 bg-[#fffaf7] px-5 py-4 text-sm outline-none ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#a7295a]/30" /></label>
              <label class="block rounded-[24px] bg-white/88 p-4 ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/16"><span class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-sm font-bold">한자</span><span class="rounded-full bg-[#f6f0ea] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-[#7a6f6a]">선택</span></span><input name="hanjaName" placeholder="金民秀" maxlength="3" class="w-full rounded-[18px] border-0 bg-[#fffaf7] px-5 py-4 text-sm outline-none ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#a7295a]/30" /></label>
              <label class="block rounded-[24px] bg-white/88 p-4 ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/16"><span class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-sm font-bold">생년월일</span><span class="rounded-full bg-[#f6f0ea] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-[#7a6f6a]">선택</span></span><input name="birthDate" type="date" class="w-full rounded-[18px] border-0 bg-[#fffaf7] px-5 py-4 text-sm outline-none ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#a7295a]/30" /></label>
              <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-white/88 p-4 ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/16"><div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-sm font-bold">양력 / 음력</span><span class="rounded-full bg-[#f6f0ea] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-[#7a6f6a]">선택</span></div><div class="grid gap-3"><label><input type="radio" name="calendarType" value="solar" class="peer sr-only" checked /><span class="flex justify-center rounded-[18px] bg-[#fffaf7] px-4 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[#5f5a57] ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 peer-checked:bg-[#7fe6db] peer-checked:text-[#003e39] peer-checked:ring-0">양력</span></label><label><input type="radio" name="calendarType" value="lunar" class="peer sr-only" /><span class="flex justify-center rounded-[18px] bg-[#fffaf7] px-4 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[#5f5a57] ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 peer-checked:bg-[#7fe6db] peer-checked:text-[#003e39] peer-checked:ring-0">음력</span></label></div></div>
              <div class="rounded-[24px] bg-white/88 p-4 ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/16"><div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-sm font-bold">성별</span><span class="rounded-full bg-[#f6f0ea] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-[#7a6f6a]">선택</span></div><div class="grid gap-3"><label><input type="radio" name="gender" value="female" class="peer sr-only" checked /><span class="flex justify-center rounded-[18px] bg-[#fffaf7] px-4 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[#5f5a57] ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 peer-checked:bg-[#a7295a] peer-checked:text-white peer-checked:ring-0">여성</span></label><label><input type="radio" name="gender" value="male" class="peer sr-only" /><span class="flex justify-center rounded-[18px] bg-[#fffaf7] px-4 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[#5f5a57] ring-1 ring-[#b1aca8]/15 peer-checked:bg-[#a7295a] peer-checked:text-white peer-checked:ring-0">남성</span></label></div></div>
              <div data-payment-note class="rounded-[20px] border border-[#ead8d2] bg-white/70 px-4 py-4 text-sm leading-7 text-[#6d6360]">프리미엄 전체 리포트는 결제 후 열립니다. 결과 메일은 폴라 결제 시 입력한 이메일로 발송됩니다.</div>
              <button type="button" data-action="suite" class="w-full rounded-[22px] bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#a7295a,#c83b74)] px-4 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-[0_20px_35px_rgba(167,41,90,0.26)] disabled:cursor-wait disabled:opacity-60">프리미엄 결제 후 분석 시작</button>
            </form>
          </article>
          <article class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-[30px] bg-[#fffdfb] p-5">
              <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#a7295a]">Current Analysis</p>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold" style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans','Pretendard',sans-serif;" data-current-name>이름 입력 대기</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#5f5a57]" data-current-hanja>(한자 입력 대기)</p>
              <div class="mt-6 rounded-[24px] bg-[#7fe6db]/30 px-5 py-4"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3"><div><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#005a54]">Harmony Score</p><p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#005a54]" data-current-score>--</p></div><div class="rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-[#005a54]" data-current-grade>분석 대기</div></div></div>
              <div class="mt-6 space-y-3">
                <div class="rounded-[22px] bg-[#f6f0ea] p-4"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#5f5a57]">현재 진행</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-current-summary>이름 입력 후 시작하면 이름풀이, 개명추천, 개명풀이가 순서대로 채워집니다.</p></div>
                <div class="rounded-[22px] bg-[#fff7cb] p-4"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#655d00]">ManyTool AI 도사 평가</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-dosa-evaluation>현재 이름의 기운과 인상을 읽어주는 프리미엄 총평이 이 영역에 표시됩니다.</p></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section class="mt-14 grid gap-8 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.15fr)_minmax(320px,0.85fr)]">
      <section class="rounded-[36px] bg-[#f6f0ea] p-6">
        <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.8fr)_minmax(0,1.2fr)]">
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#a7295a]">이름풀이 분석</p><h3 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold" data-analysis-name>분석 결과 대기</h3><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-analysis-explanation>현재 이름의 구조와 흐름을 성명학 기준으로 정리해 드립니다.</p></article>
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-[#ede7e2] p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#5f5a57]">오격 상세</p><div class="mt-4 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2" data-analysis-grid><div class="rounded-[22px] bg-white px-4 py-4 text-sm text-[#5f5a57]">천격, 인격, 지격, 외격, 총격 결과가 이 영역에 정리됩니다.</div></div></article>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#005a54]">음 / 오행 분석</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-element-analysis>한자를 입력하면 음과 오행 흐름이 같이 정리됩니다.</p></article>
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#a7295a]">획수 분석 (수리오행)</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-stroke-analysis>획수와 오격 배치를 바탕으로 수리오행 흐름을 설명합니다.</p></article>
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#655d00]">발음 / 음운 분석</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-sound-analysis>이름의 호흡감과 발음 인상을 읽어드립니다.</p></article>
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#7a4d1f]">의미 해석 (스토리)</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-meaning-story>각 한자의 뜻과 키워드를 이어서 이름의 메시지를 풀어냅니다.</p></article>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6"><div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between gap-3"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#005a54]">개명추천 6개</p><p class="text-xs text-[#6d6360]">추천 이름마다 한글, 한자, 이유, 뜻풀이를 함께 보여드립니다.</p></div><div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3" data-recommend-list><article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6 text-sm text-[#5f5a57]">통합 분석을 시작하면 개명추천 카드가 이 영역에 채워집니다.</article></div></div>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,0.9fr)]">
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-white p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#a7295a]">상세 이름 풀이</p><h3 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold" data-report-name>상세 리포트 대기</h3><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-report-explanation>현재 이름 기준의 상세 풀이가 표시됩니다.</p></article>
          <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-[#fff7cb] p-6"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#655d00]">한자 해석</p><div class="mt-4 space-y-3" data-report-points><div class="rounded-[22px] bg-white px-4 py-4 text-sm text-[#5f5a57]">각 글자의 뜻, 획수, 오행, 키워드가 이 영역에 정리됩니다.</div></div></article>
        </div>
        <section class="mt-6 rounded-[30px] bg-white p-6 shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(48,46,43,0.05)]">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#a7295a]">AI 도사 한마디</p>
              <h3 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#2f2a28]">이름 심층 풀이</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-[#fff7cb] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-[#7a5d00]">재미로 보는 AI 참고 해석</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-dosa-rich>이름 분석을 시작하면 AI 도사 한마디와 세부 해석이 이 영역에 채워집니다.</p>
          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <article class="rounded-[24px] bg-[#fdf7f3] p-5"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#a7295a]">한자 / 음 / 오행 분석</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-detail-hanja-element>한자를 입력하면 한자, 독음, 오행 흐름이 연결됩니다.</p></article>
            <article class="rounded-[24px] bg-[#f6f0ea] p-5"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#5f5a57]">획수 분석 (수리오행)</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-detail-stroke>획수와 오격 구조가 이 영역에 정리됩니다.</p></article>
            <article class="rounded-[24px] bg-[#eaf9f6] p-5"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#005a54]">음양 균형</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-detail-yinyang>음양 균형 분석이 이 영역에 정리됩니다.</p></article>
            <article class="rounded-[24px] bg-[#fff7cb] p-5"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#7a5d00]">발음 / 음운 분석</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-detail-sound>발음과 음운 흐름이 이 영역에 정리됩니다.</p></article>
            <article class="rounded-[24px] bg-[#fffaf7] p-5 md:col-span-2"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#7a4d1f]">의미 해석 (스토리)</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]" data-detail-story>한자 뜻이 연결된 이름 스토리가 이 영역에 정리됩니다.</p></article>
            <article class="rounded-[24px] bg-[#302e2b] p-5 text-white md:col-span-2"><p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-white/70">사주 보완 연결</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/80" data-detail-saju>생년월일과 성별을 함께 넣으면 부족 오행 보완형 사주 풀이로 자연스럽게 이어집니다.</p></article>
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>
      <aside class="space-y-6">
        <section class="rounded-[32px] bg-white p-6"><h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">프리미엄 리포트 구성</h3><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-[#5f5a57]"><li>성명학 기반 이름풀이 분석</li><li>추천 이름 6개와 추천 이유</li><li>음, 오행, 수리오행, 의미 해석</li><li>ManyTool AI 도사 총평</li></ul></section>
        <section class="rounded-[32px] bg-[#a7295a] px-7 py-8 text-white"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/75">Saju Expansion</p><h3 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold">사주 보완 연결</h3><p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-white/80" data-saju-summary>생년월일과 양력·음력, 성별 입력은 다음 단계에서 부족 오행 보완 추천으로 이어질 수 있게 준비되어 있습니다.</p><a href="/ai-manseryeok" class="mt-6 inline-flex rounded-full bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-[#a7295a]">사주 결과와 연결하기</a></section>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline define:vars={{ rawApiBase }}>
  const API_BASE=(rawApiBase||(window.location.hostname==='127.0.0.1'||window.location.hostname==='localhost'?'http://127.0.0.1:8787':'')).replace(/\/+$/,'');
  const CHECKOUT_AMOUNT=4900,CHECKOUT_CURRENCY='KRW',ORDER_STORAGE_KEY='manytool.namePremium.orderId',FORM_STORAGE_KEY='manytool.namePremium.form',PENDING_RUN_KEY='manytool.namePremium.pendingRun';
  const panelTitleMap={heaven:'천격',human:'인격',earth:'지격',outer:'외격',total:'총격'};
  const gradeToneMap={대길:'매우 안정적인 길수 흐름',길:'전반적으로 무난한 길수 흐름',보통:'강점과 보완이 함께 보이는 흐름',주의:'보완 포인트가 먼저 보이는 흐름'};
  const $=(s)=>document.querySelector(s),actionButton=$('[data-action="suite"]'),paymentNote=$('[data-payment-note]'),loadingOverlay=$('[data-loading-overlay]'),loadingTitle=$('[data-loading-title]'),loadingText=$('[data-loading-text]');
  let paymentMode='mock',currentOrderId=null,paymentReady=false,currentOrderLock=null,paymentResetReason='';
  const setText=(s,t)=>{const e=$(s);if(e)e.textContent=t;},setHtml=(s,h)=>{const e=$(s);if(e)e.innerHTML=h;};
